I don't feel inadequate in anything, as I followed the 3 P's. I don't waste time on meaningless tasks, as I followed the 3 P's. My father couldn't of taught me better. Without adequacy comes arrogance, one might say. I believe he's doing quite well now, though. It's all more proof that people can improve.
